  "description": "<p><strong>“这是来自万米高空的邮件，详情稍后发回。”3日下午，本报编辑部邮箱收到了一封特殊的邮件。记者在北京飞往成都的国航CA4108航班上，利用机舱内的无线网络信号向地面发送邮件。</strong>当日，我国首个提供机上全球卫星通讯互联网服务的航班成功试飞。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e2c30d1/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243404.htm&amp;t=%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E9%A6%96%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243404.htm&amp;t=%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E9%A6%96%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243404.htm&amp;t=%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E9%A6%96%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243404.htm&amp;t=%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E9%A6%96%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%9E%E5%BD%95\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243404.htm&amp;t=%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E9%A6%96%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%92%E8%81%94%E7%BD%91%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E2%80%9D%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C