  "description": "<p><strong>雅虎的收购步伐没有停止。本周三，雅虎宣布收购Xobni，这是一家成立7年的公司，制作地址薄程序和插件，它可以强化雅虎邮箱业务。</strong>Xobni从用户所有账号处索引邮件，然后创建一个地址簿，显示各联系人的资料，包括图片、工作职位、邮件历史，甚至包括联系人在Facebook、Twitter的帖子。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e2c30cf/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243402.htm&amp;t=%E9%9B%85%E8%99%8E%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E9%82%AE%E7%AE%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E7%B0%BF%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Xobni+%E7%BA%A63000%E4%B8%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243402.htm&amp;t=%E9%9B%85%E8%99%8E%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E9%82%AE%E7%AE%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E7%B0%BF%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Xobni+%E7%BA%A63000%E4%B8%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243402.htm&amp;t=%E9%9B%85%E8%99%8E%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E9%82%AE%E7%AE%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E7%B0%BF%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Xobni+%E7%BA%A63000%E4%B8%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243402.htm&amp;t=%E9%9B%85%E8%99%8E%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E9%82%AE%E7%AE%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E7%B0%BF%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8Xobni+%E7%BA%A63000%E4%B8%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243402.htm&amp;t=%E9%9B%85%E8%99%8E%E6%94%B6%E8%B4%AD%E9%82%AE%E7%