  "description": "<p>据国外媒体报道，在经过了长达数月的寒冬后，我们终于迎来了期待已久的夏天。不过，虽然夏天相比冬季更受到人们欢迎，但这一季节也伴随着自己的问题，其中首当其冲的便是过热、脱水以及晒伤。对此，美国知名科技媒体Mashable就针对这些问题为我们列举出了14个可以助你安全度过夏天的科技小玩意儿。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e2c30ce/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243401.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D14%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%B0%8F%E7%8E%A9%E6%84%8F%E5%84%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243401.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D14%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%B0%8F%E7%8E%A9%E6%84%8F%E5%84%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243401.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D14%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%B0%8F%E7%8E%A9%E6%84%8F%E5%84%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243401.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D14%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%AF%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%BA%A6%E5%A4%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%B0%8F%E7%8E%A9%E6%84%8F%E5%84%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243401.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D14%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%AF%E5%